item.description:
There have been changes made to the original post:

Come for an introductory bird watching trip on May 16th from 10:30 to noon with the Greater Worcester Humanists. Team GWH is covering the West Boylston area for Mass Audubon's 2009 Bird-A-Thon. No experience necessary, dress for the weather and insects! Meet at 211 Temple street West Boylston (route 140) at the Mass Fish & Game sign by 10:30 am sharp.
item.how_to_find_us: 211 Temple Street, West Boylston (route 140) at the Mass Fish & Game sign
item.name: Join other GWH members for Mass Audubon's Bird-a-thon 2009
